@startuml phase3_queue
title Phase 3 — Queue Handoff & Response

participant Browser
participant Orchestrator
participant "Order Queue" as OQ
participant "Order Executor" as OE

note over Orchestrator : All agent responses\nhave been collected

Orchestrator -> OQ : enqueue order
Orchestrator --> Browser : order_status (async)

note over Browser, OQ : Browser receives response;\nqueue processing continues asynchronously

OQ -> OE : dequeue & execute
@enduml
